-<+><div class=\"story\">\r\n<h1>&#65279;</h1>\r\n<div class=\"path\">stories/TC_006_UOP.story</div>\r\n<div class=\"scenario\">\r\n<h2>Scenario: TC_001_UOP UOP Create Incoming</h2>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">Given  I navigate to 'http://172.16.30.82:8888/login.aspx'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I login as 'alaa.abdelbagi' with password 'Aa1'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Add Process Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Incoming Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">When  Set 'Subject Field' value to 'random'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  Set 'Num Book From The Source' value to 'nanotime'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '2 | &#1608;&#1581;&#1583;&#1577; &#1575;&#1604;&#1585;&#1602;&#1575;&#1576;&#1577;' from the 'Incoming Commissioner Destination' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '1 | &#1608;&#1586;&#1575;&#1585;&#1577; &#1575;&#1604;&#1578;&#1585;&#1576;&#1610;&#1577;' from the 'Source Book By Name' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '4' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  Select 'Head Of Artistic' value from 'Receiver Name'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '4' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '1578 | &#1575;&#1585;&#1575;&#1605;&#1603;&#1587;' from the 'Delivery' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Draft Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '3' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'Incoming Commissioner Destination' and save it as 'ComboBoxValue'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get text from 'Subject Field' and save it as 'SubjectText'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'Incoming Get Serial Number' and save it as 'Incomi